  "3012980": {
    "name": "Moorhuhn Kart 4",
    "steam_appid": 3012980,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012980/extras/e62140f0e81b2a4730fe036d26c7af83.avif?t=1755522359\" width=600 height=125 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>An all-new installment!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leap into your kart and jump into the fastest poultry race of all time. This ultimate championship title chase offers you a brand new racing experience,  with improved driving physics, revised cartoon graphics and head-over-wheels loops, alongside crossplay and online multiplayer too.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012980/extras/4934eb0342560421282f14b010d4fcce.avif?t=1755522359\" width=600 height=125 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Full speed, awesome action!</strong> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Criss-cross and drive head-over-heels through the Moorhuhn universe: discover <strong>adventurous tracks</strong> with unique challenges and hidden shortcuts.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Configure your karts</strong> and use all kinds of tricks to gain the upper hand over your opponents! Choose from <strong>12 new and revised items</strong>, such as the tried and tested 16 ton weight.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Compete against crazy chickens and other well-known characters to prove you're the fastest driver around. There's even a new character - <strong>Midnight, the friendly bat</strong>.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Now with <strong>cross-platform online multiplayer</strong> for up to 8 players, letting you connect with your friends, or find new rivals from the community.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Local multiplayer</strong>:  play with up to 4 players on a single screen and experience the racing spectacle together.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Single player</strong> and <strong>Grand Prix</strong> modes against AI opponents. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race against the clock in <strong>Time Trials</strong>, every millisecond counts! Secure your spot on the <strong>Online Leaderboards</strong> – or break your own records offline and perfect every curve.   </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3012980/extras/358e8d803637b672d825a3f530cc6f81.avif?t=1755522359\" width=600 height=125 /></span></p>",
